related_questions.question: Is Office Depot the same as OfficeMax?
related_questions.snippet: OfficeMax. OfficeMax is an American office supplies retailer founded in 1988. It is now a subsidiary of Office Depot, Inc., which is headquartered in Boca Raton, Florida. ... On February 20, 2013, an all-stock merger between Office Depot and OfficeMax was announced.
